`★ Insight ─────────────────────────────────────`
- `DifficultyTier` (old 5-tier system) is being replaced by a 2-mode structure: Exploration (no survival) + Survival (4 sub-difficulties). The spec §37 describes this exactly — the old `normal/hard/brutal/ultra-brutal` tiles map cleanly to `gentle/standard/harsh/ironwood`.
- `generateSeedPhrase(Date.now())` is the right shuffle call — the function accepts an entropy number and uses `createRNG(seed)` internally. No need to call `scopedRNG` here since we want a brand-new random phrase, not a deterministic one.
- The JSX component can't safely be unit-tested (RN JSX runtime crash pattern), so pure-function exports and type shape tests are the right approach.
